short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a button to YouTube playlist pages to create a tier list.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: YouTube Playlist Tier List Maker is a handy Chrome extension that enhances your YouTube experience by allowing you to easily create tier lists from any YouTube playlist. Whether you're a content creator, a playlist curator, or simply a YouTube enthusiast, this extension simplifies the process of ranking and organizing your favorite videos.
